I gave him a bill in chancery to copyit should have
been done a week ago, and if not filed to-day, will be too
late. I should have reminded him of it, but he is so
susceptible
and irritable when I speak to him of anything, that
I abstained from doing so, supposing he had copied it,
perhaps
,
when I was not in the room. To-day I ask him for
