He was first cut by all his brother officers, and then tried
by a Court Martial. His misconduct was as undeniable as
it was unpardonable. He was cashiered, and left the place,
degraded and ruined forever. Where he is now, I know not.
What
he is, I have told you. The subject is a painful one
to me, for I know the unfortunate, weak-minded young
man's father, and had wished to save him.
I thank your lordship, replied Lennox, after a pause.
The earl smiled. Middleton breathed more freely, and
